= wip site for agile france 2010

extracted some pages from http://xpday.fr/
content is not relevant at this time for 2010 conference

= run demo
install ruby, >= 1.9.1p129 recommended
install gem

>gem install sinatra
>ruby site.rb

turn of network
go to http://localhost:4567 from browser

= note
  <scripts> are not rendered by webrick, which is default server, unless more is installed (mongrel for instance, did not tried)

= insights
  have some test
  lessen duplication in html source => compose views
  use coc so that images are discovered from conventioned location images/sponsors for instance